API Endpoints for User Screens
Authentication

POST /auth/signup
Registers a new user.
POST /auth/login
Authenticates the user and returns a JWT.
User Profile

GET /users/profile
Fetches user profile details.
PUT /users/profile
Updates user profile details.
Shop Search

GET /shops
Fetches nearby shops based on location (?location=<area>).
Orders

POST /orders
Creates a new order with selected services.
GET /orders
Fetches all orders for the logged-in user.
GET /orders/:id
Fetches details of a specific order.
Checkout

POST /orders/checkout
Processes payment and confirms the order.
GET /orders/:id/summary
Returns order summary after payment.